{"tid":1308624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【屌你班撚樣】兄弟爬山 各自努力 不分化 不割蓆","createTime":"2019-07-12T02:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T14:37:51.000Z","uid":90601,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac7318ebdf7c64f0d404575cc9c00031dd1c357","tid":1308624,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記69 612 71一直落黎<br />\n係點樣行到今時今日呀？<br />\n你地笑鳩黑警撕label都要full gear係驚弓之鳥<br />\n大家係咁屌鳩儂牆會破壞抗爭又何嘗唔係小題大做？<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆從來都唔係主線<br />\n差佬藍絲拆連儂牆 佢地唔會破壞做抗爭<br />\n出面巴絲起連儂牆 同樣亦唔會令抗爭消退<br />\n<br />\n真正令抗爭結束既<br />\n係大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔肯出黎 唔肯上街</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲要反對同路人做緊既野 阻止同路人去做更多野</span><br />\n咁樣抗爭先會玩完呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五大訴求 對準政權<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不分化 不割蓆<br />\n仲記唔記得呀！！！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d7f2dd414c25adc8f39403253d695308921a42f6","tid":1308624,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:44:48.000Z","msg":"推呀你老母"},{"pid":"9d24eb8c2e4efa0a9212c9d4aa7556095eb7ebec","tid":1308624,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:45:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"feec7b18c18e2f8152717e9092740170552d1404","tid":1308624,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:48:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc900e4da7524ad506aa24fa5af90f49104a24b2","tid":1308624,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:48:49.000Z","msg":"不割不分"},{"pid":"90a0198c8f1d62e7163d1e059ab0c9d95cb2d11c","tid":1308624,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:50:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd62f678d58a1f514c99311413be491caaf57fc1","tid":1308624,"uid":117892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:51:14.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推！<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾啲鬼帶走個風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比起任何事 我只求每個義士平安歸隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n釋放所有被捕示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推到有更多被捕示威者嘅消息為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/miQP3E2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmiQP3E2.png&h=952b7336&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KwADWZ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKwADWZ3.png&h=9b8499b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbfdc0eefb4085913fe7bd1f2e44ada8c86106b8","tid":1308624,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"355294badbe272a5f8c614d758dc226db3c3a88d","tid":1308624,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:58:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e552f9d687acce004cd3140280a7bb955fcb240","tid":1308624,"uid":260139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:00:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdc8aa06d1adef8ddaf1acfccc02d329e4f7b4db","tid":1308624,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:01:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a73ab47737c61bbaa4fab4636bb6ad633bd090ff","tid":1308624,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:04:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勿分化 勿指責<br />\n尊重示威者決定<br />\n基於五大訴求行事</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"651223ac16566891fb516263f65c9c41db08ee39","tid":1308624,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c018daf07d2609cba9f10246713bfc0f876e17b","tid":1308624,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:07:27.000Z","msg":"全部同我入嚟記住